my latest invention.
Here, hold this.

24:03.240 --> 24:06.152
Now, this is a safety pin.
It's really important.

24:06.160 --> 24:09.152
It's really Important
that you don't
accidentally pull this out,

24:09.160 --> 24:11.071
and then hit this lever.

24:15.480 --> 24:16.595
Hit the deck!

24:36.840 --> 24:37.875
Whoa.

24:38.800 --> 24:43.555
Uh... So, gotta...
You know, dinner.

24:46.880 --> 24:49.599
B e!
y

24:49.600 --> 24:54.469
Well, that sucks,
