24:59.880 --> 25:00.915
Where's Elspeth?

25:01.360 --> 25:04.158
lthought she was
upstairs with you.
Can you go get her?

25:09.720 --> 25:10.835
Hey!

25:10.840 --> 25:12.717
The papier-maché is
off limits to aliens!

25:12.720 --> 25:14.517
You're the alien
on this crew, buddy.

25:14.520 --> 25:16.556
This structure's
simple molecular composition

25:16.560 --> 25:19.313
makes it very suitable
for rapid energy conversion.

25:19.320 --> 25:23.313
I don't care if
it's vitamin-filled.
I need to take this to school.

25:23.320 --> 25:26.676
Rod, there is much
more at stake here
than just your volcano.

25:26.680 --> 25:28.636
Really? Like...

25:30.640 --> 25:32.119
What was that?

25:32.120 --> 25:35.237
Some rude bud-plucker
stumbled in
without an invite.

25:35.240 --> 25:39.836
I'll set up the brain-wiper
to erase its mind,
assuming it's got one.

25:45.240 --> 25:48.516
Did you really have
to do whatever this is?
What?

25:48.520 --> 25:50.954
Would you have preferred
total disintegration?

25:51.160 --> 25:54.072
Ooh. That's my favorite.
A little...
Problem solved.

25:54.080 --> 25:56.833
You need
to unfreeze her.
Now!

25:56.840 --> 25:59.149
Will you vouch
for her cooperation?

25:59.160 --> 26:00.593
Cooperation?

26:00.600 --> 26:04.115
Look, okay,
so they're aliens,

26:04.120 --> 26:05.599
but they need a place
to repairtheir ship,

26:05.600 --> 26:07.192
and can't let anyone
know that they're here.

26:07.200 --> 26:08.918
So, they came
to me for help.

26:08.920 --> 26:09.955
You?

26:10.720 --> 26:14.872
lfyou promise
not to tell anyone,
they'll let you go.

26:14.880 --> 26:17.474
Okay?
Okay, okay!

26:18.160 --> 26:19.832
Agreed?
Agreed.

26:19.840 --> 26:22.991
Captain Grakker,
reverse the polarity.

26:26.080 --> 26:30.278
Don't do anything stupid!
Me? How about them?

26:30.680 --> 26:34.639
They're way ahead of us,
Elspeth. They flew here
in a starship.

26:36.560 --> 26:39.074
