Who goes there?

39:35.200 --> 39:36.269
Busted!

39:38.280 --> 39:39.793
Execute Plan 'B'!

39:39.800 --> 39:40.994
Begin Operation Cover-up.

39:46.320 --> 39:48.117
Sorry, guys. Be quiet.

39:52.480 --> 39:53.595
Ooh. Hello.

39:53.600 --> 39:54.749
Hi, Aunt Gwen.

39:54.920 --> 39:56.433
We're having quiet time.

39:57.240 --> 39:59.037
Mmm. Amazing.

40:08.240 --> 40:10.117
What's this?

40:20.560 --> 40:22.596
Are the little aliens
all done with these?

40:22.760 --> 40:26.150
Yep.
Mission accomplished.

40:27.000 --> 40:30.629
I'll just bring them
back to the kitchen, then.

40:32.560 --> 40:34.551
Carry on.
Will do, Aunt Gwen.

40:34.560 --> 40:35.675
Hmm.

40:41.200 --> 40:42.679
That was close.

40:47.440 --> 40:50.398
All right, class.
Before we get started
this afternoon,

40:50.400 --> 40:53.358
I'll go ahead
and collect
your math worksheets.

40:53.360 --> 40:54.713
Thank you.

40:54.720 --> 40:56.039
You good in there?

40:56.040 --> 40:57.473
It's pretty good, yeah.
Thank you.

40:57.480 --> 40:58.799
