harder to believe than that?

49:42.840 --> 49:47.789
Billy, my archenemy,
the rotten,
lying little kid.

49:48.560 --> 49:51.028
He's a fugitive mastermind
from another planet,

49:51.040 --> 49:53.474
wanted across the galaxy
for his hideous crimes.

49:53.480 --> 49:56.711
And?
So, what's that say
about my life?

49:56.720 --> 49:59.314
I mean,
a lot of kids get bullied
