is to be cruel.

58:47.000 --> 58:48.991
In the civilized galaxy,

58:49.000 --> 58:52.356
cruelty to others is
the greatest crime of all,

58:52.360 --> 58:55.875
and B'KR is
the greatest criminal
of them all.

58:55.880 --> 58:58.678
Millions have wept.

58:58.680 --> 59:01.274
There's got to be
a way to stop him.
