59:01.280 --> 59:05.637
The flashing countdown thingy
shows how long we have
till yourworld

59:05.640 --> 59:07.949
and the prison
planetoid align in,

59:07.960 --> 59:11.191
like, a dimensional web
that is really complicated,

59:11.200 --> 59:13.839
and you'll
never understand it,

59:13.840 --> 59:18.436
but that's when B'KR
will need an Activator
to make his hypertunnel.

59:18.440 --> 59:20.749
So, if we find
an Activator...

59:20.760 --> 59:23.957
Then we can destroy it
before he gets a chance
to create the tunnel.

59:23.960 --> 59:27.191
And the galactic
super criminals won't
be able to invade Earth.

59:27.200 --> 59:32.991
In 58 minutes,
3.2 seconds from now,
more or less.

59:33.000 --> 59:35.150
So, how do we find
an Activator?

59:35.160 --> 59:37.628
It'll be close to
the dimensional disruption

59:37.640 --> 59:39.198
that's causing
your strange weather.

59:41.040 --> 59:42.519
