Captain, there's only
one course of action
that we can take.

01:01:33.080 --> 01:01:34.149
Surrender.

01:01:34.160 --> 01:01:35.957
What?
What?

01:01:35.960 --> 01:01:39.999
Well, according
to the Galactic Code,
all larva must be protected.

01:01:40.000 --> 01:01:43.834
Remember, all is not lost
until all is lost.

01:01:43.840 --> 01:01:46.673
Aren't you
a ray ofsunshine?
Yeah.

01:01:49.720 --> 01:01:51.676
B'KR, hear my words.

01:01:51.680 --> 01:01:55.355
We will surrender,
but only if
you free the larva.

01:01:55.640 --> 01:01:58.154
Done. Now, get in here.

01:02:03.160 --> 01:02:04.593
Open sesame seed.

