My scans show
six crew onboard,

01:02:39.120 --> 01:02:41.873
so, I want all six
to surrender, no weapons,

01:02:41.880 --> 01:02:44.553
and then I'll release
my captives.

01:02:44.560 --> 01:02:48.348
Shutting down
all systems ASAP.

