lthought
I recognized you
at school.

01:04:00.800 --> 01:04:02.995
We have a deal, B'KR!

01:04:20.080 --> 01:04:22.071
That tickled!
Again!

01:04:42.280 --> 01:04:44.396
What a stimulating
collection of artifacts.

01:04:44.720 --> 01:04:47.757
The intellect that chose them
must be of the highest order.

01:04:47.760 --> 01:04:49.637
Linda's always messing
with my stuff.

01:04:51.280 --> 01:04:53.111
Status report,

01:04:53.560 --> 01:04:56.279
lam harshed,
yet retain my mellowness.

01:04:56.280 --> 01:04:58.589
I am fully operational.

01:04:58.600 --> 01:05:01.797
I'm not. This place
is a mess, Rod.

01:05:01.800 --> 01:05:04.712
Ow! I hit something
really hard.

01:05:06.440 --> 01:05:07.873
What the heck is
this thing, anyway?

01:05:08.960 --> 01:05:10.075
Plink!

01:05:10.080 --> 01:05:12.310
Flibblx be honored!
It is a Warrior Miracle!

01:05:12.320 --> 01:05:14.914
Rod, you've found
the missing piece
of the embiggener.

01:05:15.880 --> 01:05:18.155
The Hippo
Marsupial Weathervane?

01:05:18.360 --> 01:05:20.874
Hydrocoptic... Never mind.

01:05:21.080 --> 01:05:24.038
Linda must've shoved it
in here the day
you trashed my window.

01:05:24.280 --> 01:05:27.750
All we have to do now
to enlarge the Ferkel
and ourselves...

01:05:27.760 --> 01:05:31.036
Is put the Vane back
in its proper place
on the outside of the ship.

01:05:31.040 --> 01:05:33.235
We're locked inside
a smelly backpack.

01:05:33.240 --> 01:05:35.549
How are we going to
get back on the Ferkel?

01:05:35.560 --> 01:05:37.596
As Warrior Science
teaches us,

01:05:37.600 --> 01:05:40.797
PIanjite-fribble wasn't
smelled with a single sniff.

01:05:40.800 --> 01:05:42.472
Mmm-hmm.

01:05:42.880 --> 01:05:43.869
True.

01:05:59.600 --> 01:06:01.318
Time to shake things up.

01:06:04.600 --> 01:06:05.749
What's he doing?

01:06:05.760 --> 01:06:06.988
Shaking us!

01:06:07.000 --> 01:06:08.274
Why?

01:06:08.280 --> 01:06:10.794
He probably thinks
it's funny.

01:06:10.800 --> 01:06:12.518
Millions have wept.

01:06:12.520 --> 01:06:14.158
Make that
a million and one.

01:06:57.920 --> 01:06:59.512
This Is our chance to escape.

01:06:59.800 --> 01:07:02.155
How? We're upside
down on the flap.

01:07:02.160 --> 01:07:05.869
Warrior Science teaches us
that when there is
no other choice...

01:07:05.880 --> 01:07:09.316
We make the choice we must.

01:07:09.520 --> 01:07:11.909
The Berserker Module.

01:07:17.280 --> 01:07:19.510
Captain Grakker,
are you ready?

01:07:19.520 --> 01:07:22.671
Madame Pong,
lam a Friskian fighter.

01:07:22.680 --> 01:07:25.672
I was ready
the day I was extruded
from the vats.

01:07:30.320 --> 01:07:33.630
Time to get
this party started.

01:07:42.760 --> 01:07:45.399
Everyone back.

01:07:51.880 --> 01:07:53.916
Grakker! Bad wall!

01:07:54.280 --> 01:07:56.316
Bad wall! Kill!

01:07:57.440 --> 01:08:00.716
Bad wall! Bad wall!
Die, die!

01:08:06.440 --> 01:08:08.271
Oh-ho! Yes.

01:08:34.319 --> 01:08:37.835
The sap is rising.

01:08:40.399 --> 01:08:42.197
Ohh.

01:08:42.200 --> 01:08:44.839
That feels good.

01:08:56.160 --> 01:08:59.310
Oh! Look who's gone to seed.

01:08:59.319 --> 01:09:02.915
Now, feel the fury
of the Ferkel's
fearsome fighter!

01:09:02.920 --> 01:09:04.353
Kreegah!

01:09:10.359 --> 01:09:12.157
Kreegah!

01:09:16.680 --> 01:09:17.715
Kreegah!

01:09:19.600 --> 01:09:21.078
We're not on solid ground!

01:09:21.080 --> 01:09:23.832
Grakker! No!
The wall is dead!

01:09:27.399 --> 01:09:28.719
Brace for impact!

01:09:46.399 --> 01:09:49.790
The mighty Grakker triumphs!
Bad wall dead! Kreegah!

01:09:51.600 --> 01:09:53.830
Rod, Elspeth, quickly!

01:09:57.280 --> 01:09:58.474
Who's next?

01:09:58.480 --> 01:09:59.549
Uh-oh.

01:10:00.920 --> 01:10:01.909
Oh, no.

01:10:15.880 --> 01:10:17.313
We've got to get
you guys out of here!

01:10:17.320 --> 01:10:20.517
No, young Allbright,
you have a different mission.

01:10:20.520 --> 01:10:23.512
Trust in Warrior Science!
But, Tar...

01:10:28.400 --> 01:10:30.630
Oh. Right. It's time.

01:10:30.880 --> 01:10:33.872
Phil reports
that the Ferkel is
back up to full power.

01:10:34.360 --> 01:10:36.191
It's up to you now, Rod.

01:10:36.200 --> 01:10:40.113
Hold on. Why him?
I'm the one who saw
itwas missing.

01:10:40.120 --> 01:10:44.079
Young Elspeth, each of us
has our own part
to play in this mission.

01:10:44.080 --> 01:10:47.550
And this one is something
an Allbright should do.

01:10:51.720 --> 01:10:53.950
He's getting ready
to blast the Ferkel!

01:10:53.960 --> 01:10:55.996
Phillogenous esk Piemondum!

01:10:56.480 --> 01:10:57.549
Now!

01:10:57.920 --> 01:10:59.911
It's mulching time!

01:11:09.640 --> 01:11:11.596
Ifeel the need for speed.

01:11:15.600 --> 01:11:16.589
Whoo-hoo!

01:11:24.720 --> 01:11:27.439
This is where
the rubber tree
hits the road!

01:11:27.440 --> 01:11:30.273
Rod! Elspeth!
To the Ferkel!

01:11:38.920 --> 01:11:40.114
Whoo!

01:11:40.440 --> 01:11:41.759
Whoo!

01:11:44.200 --> 01:11:45.792
I'd call this a face off,
if I had a face.

01:11:45.960 --> 01:11:49.873
I'm going to smush you
like a bug.

01:11:50.440 --> 01:11:52.271
You throw like an alien.

01:11:52.600 --> 01:11:54.158
Huh? Huh?

01:11:54.840 --> 01:11:56.159
Incoming!

01:12:03.240 --> 01:12:04.673
Cling on tight, Rod!

01:12:11.000 --> 01:12:12.956
Phil, are you there?

01:12:12.960 --> 01:12:15.269
Ready to put my petals
to the metal.

01:12:16.680 --> 01:12:17.999
Phil, steady the ship!

01:12:18.000 --> 01:12:21.037
I'm about to put
the you-know-what
in the you-know-where.

01:12:21.040 --> 01:12:22.996
You said it,
kind of, sort of.

01:12:24.640 --> 01:12:25.789
He can't!

01:12:27.600 --> 01:12:29.795
I hate these people!

01:12:34.520 --> 01:12:37.398
Rod, the hypertunnel's
trying to pull us in!

01:12:41.320 --> 01:12:43.993
I can't hold this
position much longer!

01:12:54.560 --> 01:12:56.152
Pudge-Boy.

01:13:04.720 --> 01:13:06.233
Stop right there.

01:13:06.240 --> 01:13:08.754
You of all people
can't trust
the Galactic Patrol.

01:13:08.760 --> 01:13:11.638
They've been lying to you.
What?

01:13:11.640 --> 01:13:16.236
The truth about your father...
They'll never tell you,
but I will!

01:13:16.400 --> 01:13:19.597
All you have to do
is put that down.

01:13:19.600 --> 01:13:23.036
Rod, close your earflaps.
That meatpod's the liar!

01:13:23.200 --> 01:13:25.634
Why should I trust you
and not them?

01:13:25.640 --> 01:13:27.870
I'm the only one
who can take you
to your father.

01:13:31.000 --> 01:13:33.434
Everything's gonna
be all right.

01:13:33.440 --> 01:13:34.509
Ow!

01:13:34.840 --> 01:13:37.718
I'll come back, Rod.
I promise.

01:13:40.560 --> 01:13:44.155
Simple choice, Allbright.
Yes, or no?

01:13:44.560 --> 01:13:45.709
Dad...

01:13:45.720 --> 01:13:47.551
Rod, you can't!

01:13:52.640 --> 01:13:54.073
You know it's what
you want, Allbright.

01:13:54.880 --> 01:13:58.236
It's not about me, Billy!
There's much more
at stake here!

01:13:59.840 --> 01:14:02.035
I'm an Allbright.
I can do this.

01:14:11.080 --> 01:14:14.072
The Ferkel is go!

01:14:14.440 --> 01:14:16.317
Whoo-hoo-hoo!

01:14:16.320 --> 01:14:19.596
Eat my pollen,
hypertunnel!
Yes!

01:14:29.760 --> 01:14:30.954
You did it!

01:14:31.240 --> 01:14:35.279
Come on, Elspeth. We did it!
You flew straight at B'KR
to save the Ferkel!

01:14:35.280 --> 01:14:36.998
Obviously!

01:14:37.000 --> 01:14:38.638
Urn...

01:14:38.960 --> 01:14:40.359
I don't think
we're done yet.

01:14:44.920 --> 01:14:46.797
I'm going to blast
you all to quarks!

01:14:46.800 --> 01:14:48.392
Nobody's going
to mow me down.

01:14:51.240 --> 01:14:53.117
Flower Power!

01:14:54.240 --> 01:14:55.593
Yeah! Whoo-hoo!

01:15:12.320 --> 01:15:14.072
Fasten your pod-belts!

01:15:19.840 --> 01:15:23.469
I'll show this planet wrecker
some real fun with science.

01:15:23.480 --> 01:15:26.916
Saplings,
shield your light-sensing
jelly balls.

01:15:26.920 --> 01:15:29.639
"Jelly balls"?
I think he means our eyes.

01:15:29.640 --> 01:15:30.959
Now!

01:15:39.680 --> 01:15:41.318
Dang it!

01:15:41.320 --> 01:15:43.356
Time to pluck this weed.

01:15:48.080 --> 01:15:49.593
Farewell, Ferkel!

01:15:49.600 --> 01:15:51.750
Reflect on this, B'KR.

01:15:54.760 --> 01:15:56.318
Boogers!

01:16:00.400 --> 01:16:04.678
Rod! Elspeth! Scanners say
the Activator's in B'KR's
science project.

01:16:04.680 --> 01:16:06.591
You have to nip if
in the bud.
Huh?

01:16:08.560 --> 01:16:09.595
I see it!

01:16:12.280 --> 01:16:13.952
How much time
do we have left?

01:16:13.960 --> 01:16:16.155
Three minutes and...

01:16:16.160 --> 01:16:18.833
Who knows how many seconds?
Just hurry!

01:16:18.840 --> 01:16:21.673
You have to shut it down.
What're you going to do?

01:16:26.720 --> 01:16:28.392
I'm going
to shutdown Billy.

01:16:28.400 --> 01:16:30.630
Is that the lunch bell?

01:16:30.640 --> 01:16:33.200
The gym's going to
be swarming with kids.

01:16:33.200 --> 01:16:36.033
And swarming with
galactic criminals.

01:16:37.880 --> 01:16:39.598
Phil, activate
the embiggener!

01:16:39.600 --> 01:16:41.591
Just forme.
Here you grow!

01:16:42.720 --> 01:16:43.835
Good one.

01:16:45.880 --> 01:16:47.438
Whoa. You got big.

01:17:04.520 --> 01:17:05.714
Quit it, Pudge-Boy.

01:17:05.720 --> 01:17:07.995
My name is Rod Allbright!

01:17:08.000 --> 01:17:10.355
The sprout is blossoming.

01:17:23.120 --> 01:17:26.556
Elspeth,
pull the blue wires.
Pull them all!

01:17:29.360 --> 01:17:31.590
You're ruining everything.

01:17:31.600 --> 01:17:33.397
Now, you know how it feels!

01:17:34.560 --> 01:17:35.675
Go, Rod!

01:17:38.880 --> 01:17:41.599
Rod, the galactic criminals
are almost here.

01:17:53.640 --> 01:17:56.871
Let's see you all
laugh at this, losers.

01:18:05.200 --> 01:18:06.315
What?

01:18:13.000 --> 01:18:16.913
All those brave bananas
just got creamed.

01:18:38.120 --> 01:18:40.714
The volcano?
The kid's a blooming genius.

01:18:52.480 --> 01:18:55.756
Elspeth!
One minute and counting.

01:18:57.760 --> 01:18:59.159
Rod! IngredientZ!

01:19:03.200 --> 01:19:06.033
This is the big one!

01:19:06.440 --> 01:19:07.793
Hey, Rod Allbright.

01:19:08.960 --> 01:19:12.111
Yourworld is mine.

01:19:13.680 --> 01:19:17.116
I don't like
the sound of that,
and I don't have ears.

01:19:17.440 --> 01:19:21.194
The galactic criminals
are almost here!

01:19:31.400 --> 01:19:32.958
Ten seconds.

01:19:33.560 --> 01:19:37.838
Nine, eight, seven, six,

01:19:39.040 --> 01:19:45.559
five, four, three,

01:19:45.560 --> 01:19:47.437
two,

01:19:47.640 --> 01:19:48.914
one!

01:19:48.920 --> 01:19:50.558
No!

01:19:50.560 --> 01:19:53.870
Elspeth, no time left.
Pull everything!

01:19:56.960 --> 01:19:58.473
Whoo-hoo-hoo!

01:20:01.200 --> 01:20:04.033
Whoo! I'm tired.
I need fertilizer.

01:20:18.000 --> 01:20:20.275
Time to make like
a tree and leaf.

01:20:22.600 --> 01:20:23.999
Fart burps!

01:20:36.120 --> 01:20:37.314
I saw everything.

01:20:38.920 --> 01:20:42.037
Everything?
Yeah, it was
the best volcano ever!

01:20:45.520 --> 01:20:47.351
Hey, where's Billy?
Gone.

01:20:47.360 --> 01:20:49.476
He won't be showing
his face around here again.

01:21:02.640 --> 01:21:04.915
Just like his father.

01:21:08.160 --> 01:21:11.914
I'll get a mop.
Yeah.

01:22:08.600 --> 01:22:11.637
This parting is sad
for me, Young Allbright,

01:22:11.640 --> 01:22:14.791
but I honor
the Warrior Spirit
within you and Elspeth,

01:22:14.800 --> 01:22:17.234
and wish you could
travel the stars with us.

01:22:17.240 --> 01:22:20.073
Thank you, Tar Gibbons.
We've learned a lot
from you already.

01:22:20.080 --> 01:22:22.071
At least half of it
makes sense.

01:22:22.080 --> 01:22:24.116
Let us hope
it is the right half.

01:22:24.120 --> 01:22:26.634
Oh, I don't want
to get all sappy,

01:22:26.640 --> 01:22:28.915
but even though
you're not green,

01:22:28.920 --> 01:22:33.311
you two are
fine human beans...
Uh, beings.

01:22:33.320 --> 01:22:34.435
Plink!

01:22:36.000 --> 01:22:39.993
Rod, do you know why B'KR
told you that he knows
where yourfather is?

01:22:40.000 --> 01:22:41.353
To be cruel.

01:22:41.360 --> 01:22:46.275
True, but what is also true,
is there is no way
for B'KR to know

01:22:46.280 --> 01:22:50.068
where yourfather is,
because his location
and his mission...

01:22:50.080 --> 01:22:51.718
Are classified?

01:22:51.720 --> 01:22:53.472
You mean
Rod's father is a...

01:22:53.680 --> 01:22:55.671
A member of
the Galactic Patrol.

01:22:57.480 --> 01:23:00.517
Is that why I knew how
to get the Hydrocoptic
Marzul Vane to work?

01:23:02.520 --> 01:23:05.592
Your father might have
transferred more knowledge
to you than...

01:23:09.880 --> 01:23:11.711
I've already said too much.

01:23:11.720 --> 01:23:13.358
Take heart,
young Allbright.

01:23:13.360 --> 01:23:16.079
Yourfather
would not have left
without good reason.

01:23:16.520 --> 01:23:21.116
There's always
a seed of hope. Perhaps
you'll see him again...

01:23:21.440 --> 01:23:24.079
But only when
the time is right.

01:23:24.720 --> 01:23:28.076
When the galaxy
is safe once again.

01:23:58.240 --> 01:23:59.878
You think we'll ever
see them again?

01:23:59.880 --> 01:24:01.233
I hope so.
Me, too.

01:24:01.240 --> 01:24:02.719
We're part of
the team now, right?

01:24:02.720 --> 01:24:03.835
Right.

01:24:03.840 --> 01:24:05.592
But we still need
to have that talk.

01:24:05.880 --> 01:24:08.075
Huh?
Star Wars.

01:24:08.080 --> 01:24:09.308
Star Trek.

01:24:09.320 --> 01:24:12.596
The Force beats
the Federation any day.

01:24:12.600 --> 01:24:15.637
The Klingons beat
the Rebel Alliance
any day.

01:24:15.640 --> 01:24:17.949
Warrior Science says
this isn't over.

01:24:17.960 --> 01:24:19.678
Until it's over.

01:24:19.680 --> 01:24:21.910
Hey! Guys!
Did you see that?

01:24:21.920 --> 01:24:24.912
You mean that flash
of purple light?
Yeah, what was that?

01:24:28.080 --> 01:24:31.277
The Starship Ferkel.
Part of the Galactic Patrol.

01:24:31.280 --> 01:24:35.193
Its crew are all aliens.
Its pilot is a potted plant.

01:24:37.360 --> 01:24:40.318
You guys!
I almost believed you
that time.

01:24:40.720 --> 01:24:42.517
There's always next time.

01:24:48.200 --> 01:24:51.795
You were joking
about those little aliens,
right?

01:24:51.800 --> 01:24:53.392
That's classified.

01:26:17.480 --> 01:26:23.077
"And Billy Becker was banned
from this dimension
for 50 keltrons,

01:26:23.080 --> 01:26:28.313
"stuck in a galactic prison
with no hope of getting out."

01:26:28.480 --> 01:26:30.994
Or maybe I did.

